5. At the request of the Head of the Senior People's Procuracy, the Procuracy discusses, comments on criminal cases, administrative cases, civil cases, marriage and family, and business, businessBusiness, trade, and labor for the Director to consider and decide.

Organizational structure of the provincial People's Procuracy

