c) Being convicted by the Court and judgments and decisions has taken legal effect;

d) Prohibited acts specified in Article 8 of this Law;

d) Failing to complete the task of 01 year at the appointed rank;

e) The appointed person in the rank of fraud in the rank promotion or dishonest declaration exam in the appointment dossier into the rank;

g) Other cases in accordance with the law on cadres, civil servants and public employees.

2. The Government stipulates the authority, order and procedures for dismissal of inspectors.

